desc_long								关于这款游戏							BECOME A PART OF THE CREW!  Strap in and get ready for an intense ride as you team up to take down a dangerous international gang that can only be stopped by you and the rest of the Fast & Furious crew. Get behind the wheel of some of the world’s most intense rides and take on high-stakes driving missions cooperatively with a friend or computer A.I. Put your skills to the test in Challenge Mode, an over-the-top game mode offering addictive objectives and high re-playability. Build your dream car and modify it with more than 50 awesome upgrades and performance perks. Heists, hijacks and mayhem combine across 8 epic global locations, from Rio to LA to Moscow, in an original storyline that spans the entire Fast & Furious film franchise.						
